window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For some, ghosts are no more than the wounds loved ones leave in their wake, haunting the living only with their absence. Others take a more literal view.... </p> <p>Kate Bennett, presenter of paranormal investigation cable TV show, <i>Where the Dead Walk</i>, isn't sure what she believes, other than she seems cursed to lose all those closest to her. </p> <p>After investigating a neglected cliff-top house, empty for a decade because it's \"haunted\", Kate is convinced a spirit within holds the answers to a childhood she can't remember and an unimaginable crime. </p> <p>What she can't know is that the house's owner, Sebastian Dahl, is searching for something too, and he intends to get it, whatever the cost. </p>";